PN,30301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FShared ownership schemes can be
OL,8,Fcomplex and not always fully
OL,9,Funderstood by people who enter into
OL,10,Fthem, a report from a spending
OL,11,Fwatchdog has found.
OL,13,FThe schemes offer a government-backed
OL,14,Fway to support affordable home
OL,15,Fownership for those who would struggle
OL,16,Fto buy a home outright on the open
OL,17,Fmarket.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FSchemes enable eligible buyers to
OL,8,Fpurchase a property in portions over
OL,9,Ftime, but barriers to doing this can
OL,10,Finclude cost and complexity, the
OL,11,FNational Audit Office (NAO) said.
OL,13,FComplexities with shared ownership
OL,14,Falso mean customers can get caught out
OL,15,Fby issues such as increasing service
OL,16,Fcharges, the report added.
OL,18,FIt said that limited government data
OL,19,Fmeans it is difficult to assess
OL,20,Fschemes' overall performance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe report set out how shared
OL,8,Fownership works in England, with
OL,9,Fschemes being particularly popular in
OL,10,FLondon and the South East of England.
OL,11,FIn London, shared ownership homes are
OL,12,Foften flats, it said.
OL,14,FDifferent shared ownership schemes are
OL,15,Favailable for different groups of
OL,16,Fconsumers, with eligibility rules and
OL,17,Fconditions varying.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FPeople purchase an initial share of
OL,8,Fthe property and pay rent on the
OL,9,Fremaining share to a shared ownership
OL,10,Fprovider, which could be a housing
OL,11,Fassociation, a local authority or a
OL,12,Fprivate provider.
OL,14,FOver time, shared owners can buy more
OL,15,Fof a share of the property through a
OL,16,Fprocess known as "staircasing".
OL,26,@xD@ROUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FBut complexities around service
OL,8,Fcharges and staircasing mean many who
OL,9,Ftake up the scheme do not fully
OL,10,Funderstand the longer-term financial
OL,11,Frisks, the NAO said.
OL,13,FCustomers have reported concerns such
OL,14,Fas transaction costs that apply each
OL,15,Ftime shared owners want to buy a
OL,16,Fbigger portion of their property.
OL,17,FCosts may include legal fees,
OL,18,Fvaluations and admin fees.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe report said: "As such, shared
OL,8,Fowners may opt to staircase less
OL,9,Ffrequently and with larger equity
OL,10,Fportions in each transaction."
OL,12,FIt added: "Shared owners' abilities to
OL,13,Fstaircase are also linked to house
OL,14,Fprice changes and therefore to what is
OL,15,Fhappening in the wider housing market."
OL,17,FShared owners have a long lease, with
OL,18,F"all associated obligations including
OL,19,Fpaying service charges", the report
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@oD@ROUrD@^O]tD@KOUwD@gO]zD@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FService charges are payable by tenants
OL,8,Fand leaseholders to cover the costs of
OL,9,Fmaintenance, management and services
OL,10,Fin communal areas in buildings and
OL,11,Festates.
OL,13,FThe implementation of the Renters'
OL,14,FRights Act, the Social and Affordable
OL,15,FHomes Programme and changes to
OL,16,Fleasehold are designed to improve the
OL,17,Fexperience of shared owners, but also
OL,18,Fadd to the complex picture, the report
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe report added: "Shared ownership is
OL,8,Fa complex financial and legal product
OL,9,Ffor consumers.
OL,11,F"There have been criticisms from
OL,12,Fstakeholder groups about the
OL,13,Finformation given to prospective and
OL,14,Fcurrent shared owners in the past.
OL,15,FThese criticisms included a lack of
OL,16,Finformation and concerns about
OL,17,Fincreasing costs relating to service
OL,18,Fcharges, complex lease arrangements
OL,19,Fand routes of redress."
OL,26,@oD@SOUsD@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe report added: "There is currently
OL,8,Fno standardised format or terminology
OL,9,Ffor service charges.
OL,11,F"When charges are unclear, it can be
OL,12,Fdifficult for shared owners to contest
OL,13,Fthem."
OL,15,FMore and better data would enable the
OL,16,FMinistry of Housing, Communities and
OL,17,FLocal Government (MHCLG) to determine
OL,18,Fwhether the model is affordable over
OL,19,Ftime and to assess risks across the
OL,20,Fshared ownership lifecycle, the NAO
OL,21,Fadded.
OL,26,@oD@SOUsD@AOUuD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FIt also said: "MHCLG told us that
OL,8,Fstaircasing to 100% is not the only
OL,9,Fpositive outcome of the shared
OL,10,Fownership model, and that a shared
OL,11,Fowner who buys a share and stays at a
OL,12,Fcertain level of ownership still gains
OL,13,Fstability, builds equity, and is
OL,14,Ftypically financially better off than
OL,15,Fremaining in the private rented
OL,16,Fsector."
OL,26,@oD@OOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FGareth Davies, head of the NAO, said:
OL,8,F"Shared ownership remains an important
OL,9,Froute into home ownership, but it is
OL,10,Fcomplex, and weaknesses in
OL,11,Finformation, affordability, data
OL,12,Fquality and redress mean that
OL,13,Fgovernment does not yet have a full
OL,14,Funderstanding of how the model works
OL,15,Ffor consumers."
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FSir Geoffrey Clifton-Brown, chairman
OL,8,Fof the Public Accounts Committee said:
OL,9,F"Shared ownership offers a pathway
OL,10,Finto home ownership for those who
OL,11,Fcannot afford to purchase a home on
OL,12,Fthe open market.
OL,14,F"As a chartered surveyor with a vested
OL,15,Finterest in this topic, it is wholly
OL,16,Funsatisfactory that people who have
OL,17,Frelied on shared ownership to get a
OL,18,Ffoot on the property ladder have been
OL,19,Ffaced with costs pressures and
OL,20,Fcomplexities.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"Rental increases, service charge
OL,8,Frises and, in some cases, building
OL,9,Fsafety concerns have led to
OL,10,Funsustainable costs over time, with
OL,11,Fsome owners experiencing difficulties
OL,12,Fin selling their properties.
OL,14,F"If we really want to help people own
OL,15,Ftheir own home, it is incumbent on the
OL,16,FGovernment to see how they can make
OL,17,Fthis scheme work better."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FIn January, the Government announced
OL,8,Fthat millions of leaseholders across
OL,9,FEngland and Wales stand to benefit
OL,10,Ffrom an overhaul of the leasehold
OL,11,Fsystem, with ground rents set to be
OL,12,Fcapped at #250 a year.
OL,14,FThe move marks the end of residential
OL,15,Fleaseholders paying over-the-top bills
OL,16,Ffor no clear service in return and it
OL,17,Fwill also make house sales easier for
OL,18,Fpeople whose lives have been put on
OL,19,Fhold because of ground rent terms that
OL,20,Fmake their homes hard to sell, it
OL,21,Fadded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FBut the announcement also sparked
OL,8,Fconcerns over the impacts for investor
OL,9,Fconfidence in the housing market.
OL,11,FAn MHCLG spokesperson said: "As the
OL,12,Freport rightly acknowledges, shared
OL,13,Fownership has an important role to
OL,14,Fplay in supporting households into
OL,15,Fhome ownership, who would otherwise
OL,16,Fstruggle to afford to buy.
OL,26,@sD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774400571
OL,3,CShared ownership schemes are complex
OL,4,Cand not always fully understood `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"We are aware of challenges faced by
OL,8,Fsome who have entered the scheme, but
OL,9,Fwe have already strengthened shared
OL,10,Fowners' rights, made sure there is
OL,11,Fgreater transparency and fairness of
OL,12,Fcosts, and enhanced data collection.
OL,14,F"We continue to explore what more can
OL,15,Fbe done to improve the experience of
OL,16,Fshared owners."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUxD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/16
